message.entry: Expected input to be a grayscale or truecolor (RGB) image.
Input signals with more than 3 dimensions are not supported.
Inputs must be of the same size and data types.
Array formation and parentheses-style indexing with objects of class ''{0}'' is not allowed.
Input image must be a 2-D image. You can use RGB2GRAY to convert an RGB image to a 2-D grayscale image.
''{0}'' must be a scalar or a two-element vector.
''{0}'' must be a two or three-element vector.
''{0}'' must be a two-, three-, or six-element vector.
All elements of ''{0}'' must be nonempty.
Input image must be an MxNx3 matrix.
Display rate should be greater than zero.
